  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>Buffet breakfast with eggs cooked to order 7 days per week.</li>
<li>Fine 3 course evening meal 5 days per week</li>
<li>One day lunch - credit Sfr40 per person, May, Jun &amp; Sep) in the hotel’s restaurant L’Olivier or 6 days per week (Jul-Aug)</li>
